title: Did Arizona report the highest number of Coved cases per day in January 2021?
subtitle: This is not the first time that the state of Grand Canyon has led the issues of the Inter-American Committee against Terrorism.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: Data collected by chief health statisticians indicate that Arizona led the world in the highest number of COVID-19 cases reported per person per day in early January 2021.
